=3D"text-editor.default"><h5>Solar radiation modification (SRM) is a contro=
versial proposal for reducing some of the impacts of climate change by refl=
ecting a small fraction of sunlight away from the Earth.</h5><p>While there=
 are a number of proposed techniques for reflecting sunlight through SRM, D=
egrees primarily focuses on Stratospheric Aerosol Injection (SAI). This for=
m of SRM proposes injecting tiny reflective aerosols into the upper atmosph=
ere to replicate the cooling effect of major volcanic eruptions.</p></div><=
div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-element-3fc593e elementor-widget e=
lementor-widget-image" data-id=3D"3fc593e" data-element_type=3D"widget" dat=
a-widget_type=3D"image.default"><figure class=3D"wp-caption"> <img fetchpri=
ority=3D"high" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"1447" height=3D"1536" src=3D"htt=
ps://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/SAI-infographic.png" data-s=
rc=3D"https://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/SAI-infographic.pn=
g" class=3D"attachment-full size-full wp-image-12013 lazyloaded" alt=3D"" d=
ata-srcset=3D"https://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/SAI-infogr=
aphic.png 1447w, https://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/SAI-inf=
ographic-283x300.png 283w, https://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/uploads/2023/=
10/SAI-infographic-965x1024.png 965w, https://www.degrees.ngo/wp-content/up=
loads/2023/10/SAI-infographic-768x815.png 768w"><figcaption class=3D"widget=
-image-caption wp-caption-text">Visual representation of how SRM might work=
 (this work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-=
ShareAlike 4.0 International License.)</figcaption></figure></div><section =
data-particle_enable=3D"false" data-particle-mobile-disabled=3D"false" clas=
s=3D"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-=
element-c009a55 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default el=
